{"tid":201854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最有效嘅減肥方法","createTime":"2017-04-15T05:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T21:39:16.000Z","uid":25813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d71afb12bbb1383953cbefe642360626ba83087","tid":201854,"uid":25813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:43:16.000Z","msg":"180<br />\n79kg<br />\n但係外表肥到仆街<br />\n有冇巴打可以救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27680675cedbfb919f7cf0accf983e3bd091dff1","tid":201854,"uid":96409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"lm學名"},{"pid":"6f5a4d8285494beca19682ab0810de608191ea94","tid":201854,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"紋身放血<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60777d7e3f04a5b50542afef0c7701518ae4aac9","tid":201854,"uid":25813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紋身放血<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係紋曬都冇用<br />\n知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf6b765a37554942e586fa81f5ce5cd74380096","tid":201854,"uid":80900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"游水啦！又唔多覺攰，又舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:之前係游水減肥"},{"pid":"f13b965cc5c0d7e0d0978838e76e6ffdc22e25d3","tid":201854,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"重訓加帶氧，最緊要都係飲食<br />\n汽水果汁果啲甜野一定要戒哂"},{"pid":"e5b337ce8eabe8752f365a64c60eaebc6dda3449","tid":201854,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93a333db98204149b537d48ec2fa115c2a88ad01","tid":201854,"uid":25813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>180 79唔算好肥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪淋巴塞<br />\n塊面好漲"},{"pid":"ff77d41f0301d038ff5a5a5ff586a479336c5dd5","tid":201854,"uid":19775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"學計卡路里, 每日岩岩好食夠基礎代謝(+/-10%)<br />\n少食加工嘢, 飲多啲水<br />\n<br />\n我堅持左兩個月減左10磅了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(當然有時同朋友出街食飯好難唔爆卡 但一次半次冇乜影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我減得唔算快 但唔覺得辛苦 同埋減太快唔健康<br />\n運動方面唔算多 都喺一星期做2-3日gym<br />\n打算完sem就做密啲加快進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好咁大壓力 心理質素對減肥都好重要<br />\n長遠嚟講最有效嘅減肥方法就喺培養健康生活習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f38d77234dfd99595505f47da935e86156b52ad","tid":201854,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"做下gym, 平板支撐有幫助"},{"pid":"b1551469462597a0482e31612a402ea1782c2fb9","tid":201854,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49e65c666f5553b6fab4c1e60c248f2102a3bf77","tid":201854,"uid":25813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T21:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>180 79唔算好肥姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪淋巴塞<br />\n塊面好漲</blockquote><br />\n面形天生冇得減</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早兩年仲係v面<br />\n轉左文職一肥就肥上面"}]}